title: I Survived 500 Days in Mega Ultra Hardcore Minecraft... FINALE! Minecraft Hardcore 100 Days
author: Corinthius
description:
In this video, I attempted to survive 500 days in mega ultra hardcore minecraft! This is better than surviving 100 days in hardcore mode minecraft, even better than surviving 100 days in ultra hardcore minecraft! This is because Herobrine is back in this minecraft survival challenge!!

Break Bedrock Tutorial:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HX_ugh3xPc4 

SUBSCRIBE?
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCumndKOptTHGr6FBrUBy4YA?sub_confirmation=1 

DISCLAIMER: Herobrine was role-played by a friend who pranked me as I tried to survive 500 days in Ultra Hardcore Minecraft. This was to make the challenge a little more harder than normal UHC and hopefully be more entertaining!

100 Days of Mega Ultra Hardcore Minecraft Playlist:
